/* 顶部要固定定位   标题要居中   自定义按钮和标题要和右边微信原生的胶囊上下对齐 */
.me-index .nav-wrap {
  position: fixed;
  width: 100%;
  top: 0;
  background: #fff;
  color: #000;
  z-index: 6;
  overflow: hidden;
}
/* 背景图 */
.me-index .nav-bg-img {
  position: absolute;
  z-index: -1;
  width: 750rpx;
  height: 466rpx;
}
/* 标题要居中 */
.me-index .nav-title {
  font-size: 34rpx;
  color: #000;
  text-align: center;
}
.me-index .body{
  text-align: center;
}
.me-index .body .header .bg-img{
  width: 750rpx;
  height: 466rpx;
}
.me-index .header-info{
  position: absolute;
  z-index: 1;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
}
  .me-index .header-info .header-img{
  width: 144rpx;
}
.me-index .header-info .nickname{
  font-size: 48rpx;
  font-family: PingFang-SC-Bold, PingFang-SC;
  font-weight: bold;
  color: #2B2B2B;
}
.me-index .content .award-times{
  font-size: 32rpx;
  font-family: PingFang-SC-Bold, PingFang-SC;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #BA131D;
  margin: 70rpx 0 68rpx;
}
.award-times::before,
.award-times::after{
  display: inline-block;
  content: "";
  width: 188rpx;
  height: 6rpx;
  margin-right: 40rpx;
  background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(239, 239, 239, 1), rgba(186, 19, 29, 1));
  vertical-align: middle;
}
.award-times::after{
  transform: rotate(180deg);
  margin-right: 0;
  margin-left: 40rpx;
}

 .me-index .content .op-btn .btn{
  width: 636rpx;
  height: 116rpx;
  line-height: 116rpx;
  background: linear-gradient(360deg, #000000 0%, #2B2B2B 100%);
  font-size: 36rpx;
  font-family: PingFang-SC-Bold, PingFang-SC;
  font-weight: bold;
  color: #FFFFFF;
  margin: 0 auto;
 }
 .me-index .content .op-btn .btn:first-child{
  margin-bottom: 38rpx;
}
.me-index .footer{
  font-size: 24rpx;
  font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, PingFang SC;
  color: rgba(43, 43, 43, 0.3);
  position: absolute;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  bottom: 20rpx;
  line-height: 36rpx;
  width: 100%;
}